The latest version of Sleipnir software can be obtained 
by issuing the following Mercurial command: 

hg clone https://bitbucket.org/libsleipnir/sleipnir

The Sleipnir wiki and bug reporting system are also at
http://bitbucket.org/libsleipnir/sleipnir

Documentation about Sleipnir can be obtained from the
Sleipnir web site or built using Doxygen.

For installation instructions, see the file named INSTALL.

The file README.developer has notes for Sleipnir developers.
